ly following initiation, discontinuation or change of dosage of citalopram in patients who are stabilized on their antipsychotic regimen, and the clozapine dosage adjusted as necessary.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/66796/', '', 'Oxitriptan, Vilazodone, Vortioxetine, Tryptophan', '', 1767369485);
